title: Urban Chaos: Riot Response (PS2) (PAL) (Fabio5ilva)
description:
Urban Chaos: Riot Response (PS2) 

Region: PAL

Year: 2006

Nick Mason and the members of Unit T-Zero are charged with taking back gang-ridden New York City from various criminal masterminds in Urban Chaos: Riot Response. You play as Nick, a man returning home from military service in the not-too-distant future. He returns to find his city overrun by gang warfare. Appalled, he joins the G18 Counter Gang Division, a special organization granted emergency powers over all public services. With control over the Police, Fire Department, and Paramedics, you'll fight to save lives, property, and the future of your home.
